com.n9mtq4.logwindow.ui.attributes

Interface Textable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GuiJFrame, GuiJFrameLightWeight

    public interface Textable
    A interface that flags a ConsoleUI as having full control over the text that has been pushed to them and that the ConsoleGui can set the text that has already been sent to it.

    Created by will on 1/7/15.

    Since:
    v4.0
    See Also:
    getText(), setText(String)
